azure.auditlogs.category.description: The category of the operation.  Currently, Audit is the only supported value.

azure.signinlogs.properties.applied_cond.description: A list of conditional access policies that are triggered by the corresponding sign-in activity.

azure.signinlogs.properties.authenticati.description: The result of the authentication attempt and additional details on the authentication method.

azure.signinlogs.properties.network_loca.description: The network location details including the type of network used and its names.

azure.signinlogs.properties.resource_id.description: The identifier of the resource that the user signed in to.

azure.signinlogs.properties.risk_event_t.description: The list of risk event types associated with the sign-in.
